description: This dataset identifies Indian health care providers nationally, so that qualified health plan issuers can identify the Indian health care provider organizations and sites that are located in the service areas of their QHPs.  It includes tribal providers, urban Indian organization providers, and Indian Health Service (IHS) facilities.
